
    <h2>1. Basic Structure</h2>
    <pre><code>
&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html&gt;
  &lt;head&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;My Web Page&lt;/title&gt;
  &lt;/head&gt;
  &lt;body&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;Welcome to HTML&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
    </code></pre>

    <h2>2. Headings</h2>
    <p>HTML offers 6 levels of headings from <code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> to <code>&lt;h6&gt;</code>.</p>

    <h2>3. Links</h2>
    <p><code>&lt;a href="https://example.com"&gt;Visit Example&lt;/a&gt;</code></p>

